<main id="main-content">
  <div class="hero"><div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="tag">About</div>
    <h1>Stack Architect</h1>
    <p>Free tools that replace paid Shopify apps — server-side tracking, inventory, email, TikTok CAPI, P&amp;L reporting, and automation stability. Built for store owners tired of paying $700+/month for things that should be free.</p>
  </div></div>
  <div class="prose-wrap"><div class="prose-inner"><div class="prose">
    <h2>What Stack Architect Is</h2>
    <p>Stack Architect is a collection of six free tools and guides that collectively replace the paid Shopify apps most stores spend $500–$900 per month on. Each tool uses Make.com's free automation tier, Google Sheets, and Systeme.io's free plan to achieve the same technical outcome as paid alternatives — without any monthly subscription, developer cost, or code.</p>
    <p>The tools are free forever. Affiliate links on the site keep the resource funded — we only recommend tools we use ourselves, and they cost you nothing extra.</p>
    <h2>Why It Exists</h2>
    <p>The Shopify app ecosystem is built around recurring revenue. Tracking apps charge $149–$299/month for server-side conversion data that costs nothing to implement directly. Inventory apps charge $29–$199/month for Google Sheets sync that takes four minutes to build. Email platforms charge $150–$400/month for automation sequences that free tools replicate entirely.</p>
    <p>Stack Architect exists to show store owners that the technical outcomes they are paying for are achievable at $0 — and to give them the exact tools and guides to do it in under six minutes per workflow.</p>
    <h2>The Six Free Tools</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/capi-shield">CAPI Shield</a> — server-side tracking for Meta and Google Ads. Replaces Elevar and Triple Whale. Saves $149–$299/month.</li>
      <li><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/stocky-swap">Stocky Swap</a> — free inventory management replacing Shopify Stocky (shutting down August 2026). Saves $29–$199/month.</li>
      <li><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/tiktok-events-api-shopify">TikTok Events API</a> — free TikTok server-side tracking via Make.com. Saves $39–$299/month.</li>
      <li><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/replace-klaviyo-free">Replace Klaviyo Free</a> — Systeme.io replaces Klaviyo with unlimited emails on the free plan. Saves $150–$400/month.</li>
      <li><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/shopify-profit-loss-automation">Shopify P&amp;L Auto</a> — live profit and loss in Google Sheets. Replaces TrueProfit and BeProfit. Saves $19–$299/month.</li>
      <li><a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/autocrat-quota-fix">Autocrat Quota Fix</a> — prevents Google Apps Script quota errors that crash automations. Saves $49–$99/month.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>The Complete Kit</h2>
    <p>Store owners who want the pre-built version rather than building from the guides can purchase the <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/pro">Complete Kit for $29</a> — four ready-to-import Make.com JSON blueprints, two Google Sheets templates, and four Loom walkthroughs. Every field pre-mapped. One payment, no subscription, permanent re-download.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For support questions, reach us via the support link in the footer. For everything else, the <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/faq">FAQ</a> and <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/shopify-automation-guides">guides</a> cover most questions store owners have before deploying the stack.</p>
  </div></div></div>
</main>
<Footer variant="minimal" />
